      <title>Peter Thiel 自 2021 年以来首次出售 Palantir 价值 1.75 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/thiel-unloads-175-million-of-palantir-in-first-sale-since-2021</link>
