      <title>阿根廷省表示，锂许可证冻结仅限于新项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/lithium-permit-freeze-limited-to-new-projects-argentina-province-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷卡塔马卡省表示，法院暂停发放锂许可证的裁决只会影响新项目，Arcadium Lithium Plc 和 Posco Holdings Inc. 等公司可以继续生产金属并开发现有项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/lithium-permit-freeze-limited-to-new-projects-argentina-province-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 16:14:08 GMT</pubDate>
