    <item>
      <title>Meta 在阻止 FTC 修改隐私协议的第二次投标中失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/meta-loses-second-bid-to-thwart-ftc-s-revisions-to-privacy-pact</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 本周输掉了第二项法院裁决，该裁决试图阻止联邦贸易委员会因指控该公司违反条款而重新启动 2020 年隐私和解协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/meta-loses-second-bid-to-thwart-ftc-s-revisions-to-privacy-pact</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 13:45:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着人工智能竞争的加剧，Adobe 股价出现 2022 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/adobe-projects-lackluster-sales-with-ai-competition-intensifying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Adobe Inc. 周五下跌 14%，原因是本季度销售前景疲弱，引发了人们对新的人工智能初创公司构成竞争威胁的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/adobe-projects-lackluster-sales-with-ai-competition-intensifying</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 20:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
